{"tid":698169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]觀塘噴泉及摩頓臺活動中心天價兩億工程被否決","createTime":"2018-06-11T12:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T13:19:15.000Z","uid":63183,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"742847f54acf7bfbf6d9470511ac2ca48e7f47cd","tid":698169,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/203900_77ddf9c2faec0cb0bde58874cd9fe507.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F203900_77ddf9c2faec0cb0bde58874cd9fe507.jpg&h=d014d806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊雪盈 Clarisse Yeung<br />\n21 分鐘 &middot; <br />\n〈立務會工務小組否決天價納米工程〉<br />\n<br />\n立務會工務小組今日召開會議，否決了摩頓臺活動中心項目！會上多位立法會議員發言質詢，表示在有限空間興建活動中心效益成疑，以及排球場重置安排擾民。惟政府代表及區議會主席的回應令人失望。<br />\n<br />\n民政副局長表示待工程完成後才會監察成效，又辯稱小型會堂使用率亦甚高，無視社區設施設計參差，令市民因設施數量不足而屈就使用；區議會主席則在再三被質詢下，仍絕口不提諮詢會出席人數，只提及有9成出席者支持。<br />\n<br />\n署方承認摩頓臺排球場空間狹小，又要避開大樹，興建活動中心其實困難重重，引致成本上升。經一個多小時會議，摩頓臺活動中心及觀塘海濱音樂噴泉項目一同付諸表決，最後以16票贊成、17票反對，否決兩個項目。<br />\n<br />\n#停一停 #諗一諗<br />\n#嗰邊加山咪有地囉<br />\n#唔使咁急盲搶排球場喎"},{"pid":"1c658718208e814601bf61c4d833f2a0e349df25","tid":698169,"uid":63183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/clarisseysy/photos/a.911819232226090.1073741828.901237633284250/2002558859818783/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fclarisseysy%2Fphotos%2Fa.911819232226090.1073741828.901237633284250%2F2002558859818783%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=K1Yw%2BttpgbXCZhAh9ATRg%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=c18f44a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/clarisseysy/photos/a.911819232226090.1073741828.901237633284250/2002558859818783/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"7cc6c95d9dc4c47eccd25e902904eab0b81ef130","tid":698169,"uid":63183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"東九龍社區關注組<br />\n2小時 &middot; <br />\n[工務小組音樂噴泉速報]<br />\n<br />\n贊成16，反對17！<br />\n<br />\n我哋贏咗！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/&hellip;/c&hellip;/fc/pwsc/results/v201806111.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fc%E2%80%A6%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201806111.pdf&d=K1Yw%2BttpgbXCZhAh9ATRg%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=20177532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/&hellip;/c&hellip;/fc/pwsc/results/v201806111.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝毛孟靜、胡志偉、莫乃光、陳志全、張超雄、黃碧雲、楊岳橋、尹兆堅、朱凱廸、林卓廷、陳淑莊、許智峯、鄭松泰、鄺俊宇、譚文豪、范國威、區諾軒咁多位議員。<br />\n<br />\n#可惜今日唔係值得開心嘅日子"},{"pid":"e687b9f6a7f37443cbcd0d565172a965f9cafeb2","tid":698169,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef52fef62b91867074247d31ee6643fcb76183a0","tid":698169,"uid":2155,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"屌你係海濱整個噴水池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8b2169cc97f2f40a72f0bdf999f59871a9b4f5","tid":698169,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"好明顯 貪 2 億 嫌太少<br />\n<br />\n下次改一改啲圖則  5 億 10 億 就通過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d338699d83a01395e261a46ff96df1633fa2e27b","tid":698169,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0d3764164df72ba025f09e575ad0552a1d3333c","tid":698169,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"菲傭活動中心？"},{"pid":"bf7c47e2a2da661d518e0ab636417dfbc34e503a","tid":698169,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母世界級一流地皮起噴水池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/goo